NOTE ON BUNDLED 3D ASSETS

This MIT license covers the application source code only. The 3D model files
under `assets/` (e.g. the VF-1 Valkyrie and SD Zaku II GLB models) are
third-party, fan-made assets derived from the Macross / Robotech and Gundam
franchises. They are NOT licensed under MIT and are included for personal and
educational use only. If you redistribute this project, you are responsible for
verifying and complying with the original creators' and rights holders' terms.
"Macross" is a trademark of Big West / Tatsunoko Production.
